[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "……みんな、大丈夫かな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00487",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ユミア",
		"romanized_name": "Yumia",
		"model_path_hash": "8553801663070209956",
		"text": "きっと大丈夫だよ。みんなを信じよう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_164_038_00488",
		"still_path_hash": "3603268135404135156",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "みんな！　見て、島があるわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_038_00489",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ほんとだ……\nベップ、ここが？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00490",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "……ええ、多分そう。「九偉人図」は\nこの島の奥を指してるように見えるわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_038_00491",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "果ての大陸っていうわりには、\nぜんぜん大陸に見えないわね……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_038_00492",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ユミア",
		"romanized_name": "Yumia",
		"model_path_hash": "8553801663070209956",
		"text": "うーん、どういうことなんだろう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_164_038_00493",
		"still_path_hash": "3603268135404135156",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "魔物の気配はなさそう。どうする？　上陸する？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_038_00494",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "あ、フロッケ号が泊まったね。\n調査するみたいだし、アタシたちも上陸しよっか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00495",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ああ。何が起こるか分からないから、\nみんな油断だけはしないようにね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_038_00496",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "レスナ、ヴァレリア！　おーい！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00497",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "アルビーナ！\nみんなも無事でよかった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00498",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "「九偉人図」によると、この先が果ての大陸なのよね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00499",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そのはずよ。九偉人たちの態度もおかしいし",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00500",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "あの、皆さん、\nもしかしてこの場所をご存じなのでしょうか……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00501",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "知っていたらなんじゃ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_038_00502",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "知ってたんなら教えてよ！\n「九偉人図」なんて集める必要なかったじゃん！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00503",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "さすがにそこまでお膳立てするわけにはいかないよ。\n不相応な実力でここに来ても自分が困るだけだし？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_038_00504",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ウワッ、その通りだけど、\nシトリンに言われるとムッカムカ～！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00505",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "悪いね。そこはいくらレスナたちに協力すると\n言っても、譲れないところだったのさ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_038_00506",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "リーベ",
		"romanized_name": "Liebe",
		"model_path_hash": "281475164831455342",
		"text": "しかし……何か様子がおかしいですね。\n奥のほうに見慣れないものがあるようです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_156_038_00507",
		"still_path_hash": "5075029600051949533",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ゴゥ",
		"romanized_name": "Gou",
		"model_path_hash": "5559160385657202980",
		"text": "ああ。母様たちが何かしたのだろうが……\nとにかく行ってみよう。行ってみれば分かるとも！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_155_038_00508",
		"still_path_hash": "2242265198409136417",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]